Class Statistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractObservation
      • Observation
        • Statistics
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DateTimeComparable

    public class Statistics
extends Observation
implements DateTimeComparable
    Holds a statistic as well as data about what type of statistic it is, when it was taken, and contains methods to compare time stamps on statistics.
    Version:
    2018-12-06 Project 4
    Author:
    Elijah Boulton
